A revision of the genus Tenagobia Bergroth (Heteroptera: Corixidae)Summary Revision of the genus Tenagobia (Corixidae) in which the genus is split into seven new subgenera: Tenagobia s. str., Baliagobia, Fasciagobia, Fuscagobia, Incertagobia, Romanogobia and Schadeogobia. T. serrata Deay is synonymised with T. socialis (White) and T. hungerfordi Deay with T. schadei Lundblad. Lectotypes are designed for T. marmorata Bergroth and T. incerta Lundblad and the following new species are described: T. testacea from Colombia and Ecuador; T. campula from Per√∫; T. lundbladi from Venezuela and Colombia; T. fasciata from SE Brasil, T. balia from Brasil, Amazonas and T. aconita from Colombia.